OL,3,CPensioner couple laundered #534,000 of
OL,4,Cson's drug money while on benefits
OL,6,FA pensioner couple claimed benefits
OL,7,Fwhile laundering hundreds of thousands
OL,8,Fof pounds from their son's illegal
OL,9,Fmail-order drugs business.
OL,11,FPaul Cotson, 71, and his wife
OL,12,FStephanie, 70, invested #460,000
OL,13,Ffunnelled into their bank account by
OL,14,F43-year-old Daniel Cotson.
OL,16,FDaniel Cotson, of Marine Wharf in
OL,17,FHull, sold large quantities of
OL,18,Funlicensed class C drugs including
OL,19,Fdiazepam and temazepam online before
OL,20,Fusing local shops and post offices to
OL,21,Fmail them out across the UK.
