OL,6,FHe received more than #800,000 in bank
OL,7,Ftransfers before being arrested when
OL,8,Fstaff at a shop in Prospect Centre,
OL,9,FHull, became suspicious and called
OL,10,Fpolice in May 2021.
OL,12,FCCTV enquiries confirmed he had
OL,13,Fregularly visited the shop to send
OL,14,Fparcels.
OL,16,FA search of his home found tablets
OL,17,Fwith a street value of #44,703,
OL,18,Fcocaine worth #1,250, and #1,180 in
OL,19,Fcash.
