OL,3,CPensioner couple laundered #534,000 of
OL,4,Cson's drug money while on benefits
OL,6,FFurther investigations revealed he had
OL,7,Fmoved #534,000 to his parents' savings
OL,8,Faccount, which they used to invest in
OL,9,Ftheir own names.
OL,11,FDaniel Cotson pleaded guilty at Hull
OL,12,FCrown Court to two counts of
OL,13,Fpossessing criminal property, two of
OL,14,Fpossessing cocaine with intent to
OL,15,Fsupply, conspiracy to convert criminal
OL,16,Fproperty and supplying class C drugs.
OL,18,FHis parents, of The Link in Hull, were
OL,19,Ffound guilty of conspiracy to convert
OL,20,Fcriminal property following a four-day
OL,21,Ftrial.
