OL,6,FPC Mark Bentley, of Humberside Police,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Paul and Stephanie Cotson were
OL,8,Fnot only aware of Daniel's previous
OL,9,Fconvictions, but they actively helped
OL,10,Fhim move and invest over half a
OL,11,Fmillion pounds of criminal money. They
OL,12,Fattended his previous court hearings,
OL,13,Fknew the risks, and still chose to
OL,14,Finvolve themselves.
OL,16,F"They invested criminal proceeds in
OL,17,Ftheir own names and attempted to
OL,18,Fdistance themselves from the source of
OL,19,Fthe funds despite clear contrasting
OL,20,Fevidence."
